{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Elementos inline","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Inline_elements","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Sumário","isH3":true,"content":"<p>\"Inline\" é uma categorização dos elementos do HTML, em contraste com os <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Block-level_elements\">\"elementos de bloco\"</a>. Os elementos inline podem ser exibidos em nível de bloco ou outros elementos inline. Eles ocupam somente a largura de seu conteúdo. A diferença entre elementos inline e bloco incluem:</p>\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"modelo_de_conteúdo\">\n  Modelo de conteúdo</dt>\n <dd>\n  Geralmente, elementos inline devem ter somente dados em outros elementos inline.</dd>\n <dt id=\"formato\">\n  Formato</dt>\n <dd>\n  Por padrão, os elementos inline não começam em uma nova linha.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"elements","title":"Elementos","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Listagem dos elementos que são \"inline\":</p>\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/b\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/b\">b</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/big\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/big\">big</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/i\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/i\">i</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/small\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/small\">small</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/tt\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/tt\">tt</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/abbr\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/abbr\">abbr</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/acronym\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/acronym\">acronym</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/cite\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/cite\">cite</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/code\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/code\">code</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/dfn\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/dfn\">dfn</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/em\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/em\">em</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/kbd\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/kbd\">kbd</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/strong\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/strong\">strong</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/samp\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/samp\">samp</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/var\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/var\">var</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/a\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/a\">a</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/bdo\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/bdo\">bdo</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/br\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/br\">br</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/Img\" title=\"En/HTML/Element/Img\">img</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/map\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/map\">map</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/object\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/object\">object</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/q\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/q\">q</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/Script\" title=\"En/HTML/Element/Script\">script</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/span\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/span\">span</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/sub\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/sub\">sub</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/sup\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/sup\">sup</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/button\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/button\">button</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/Input\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/Input\">input</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/label\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/label\">label</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/select\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/select\">select</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Element/textarea\" title=\"en/HTML/Element/textarea\">textarea</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Ver também","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Block-level_elements\" title=\"en/HTML/Block-level_elements\">Elementos de nível de bloco</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"\"Inline\" é uma categorização dos elementos do HTML, em contraste com os \"elementos de bloco\". Os elementos inline podem ser exibidos em nível de bloco ou outros elementos inline. Eles ocupam somente a largura de seu conteúdo. A diferença entre elementos inline e bloco incluem:","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Inline-Elemente","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Inline elements","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Elementos en línea","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Éléments en ligne","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"インライン要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"인라인 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Elementy liniowe","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Строчные элементы","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"行内元素","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/html/inline_elements","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/html/inline_elements/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Inline_elements","title":"Elementos inline"}],"pageTitle":"Elementos inline - HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}